			</div>
			<div class="postcontent"><p>As in Be Back Soon, not the 80&#8217;s/early 90&#8217;s version&#8230; though that would be cool&#8230; hmmm.</p>
<p>Anyhow, this site is on hold for now, as I&#8217;m sure anyone paying attention still has noticed. We&#8217;ll see what happens (I have many plans, but we all know how that turns out).</p>
<p>I&#8217;ll still respond to email, and things will be left up around here, but for now there are going to be no updates until I work out exactly what I want to do with this space.</p>
<p>Until then &#8211; be well.</p>
