					<h2><a href="http://www.twilightuniverse.com/?p=364" rel="bookmark" title="DoS? Who knows&#8230;?">DoS? Who knows&#8230;?</a></h2>
					<span class="postmeta">Thursday, August 16th, 2007 | <a href="http://www.twilightuniverse.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in blog" rel="category">blog</a> |  <a href="http://www.twilightuniverse.com" title="Visit Gregory&#8217;s website" rel="external">Gregory</a> </span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="postcontent"><p>&#8230;and we&#8217;re back.</p>
<p>You might have noticed some downtime today, for some reason my site was using 40-50% of my hosts CPU. As that is somewhat crazy I can only image there was some kind of DoS or similar malicious attack against my site and a few others on this host.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ll keep you posted if I find out any more information.</p>
